710606f-a.text:

viewed eastward across the cleared westerly side of same and showing
buildings that front on the easterly side. The cleared area is the
former Vew York Railway Company yard site. The building bearing the
Spears sign, is on the south side of W. 23r Street midway between

View 3 is northeastward towards 24th Street.
